properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued January 26 at 2:49PM AKST until January 27 at 6:00PM AKST by NWS Juneau AK
properties.description:
* WHAT...Snow expected. Total snow accumulations of 4 to 6 inches.

* WHERE...Yakutat.

* WHEN...From 3 AM to 6 PM AKST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Travel could be very difficult.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...The winter storm warning will expire at 3
PM. There will be a few hours of a break in the snow before snow
showers increase once again late tonight and early Monday.
properties.instruction:
Slow down and use caution while traveling.

For the latest road conditions call 5 1 1 or visit
511.alaska.gov.

NWSheadline: WINTER STORM WARNING WILL EXPIRE AT 3 PM AKST THIS AFTERNOON... ...WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 3 AM TO 6 PM AKST MONDAY
